1T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"丁子朗與秀文、愷怡相聚上海菜館，一嚐「蒜子白肉」後，竟大膽要美女們聞口氣？子朗身形健美，原來常藉消夜增磅，秀文聞言更力邀他入團組成「瘦底」拍檔！兩位主持及後約同劉穎鏇享用日式懷石料理「八寸」，再吃肉汁豐富的「鐵板燒西班牙黑豕肉」，還有「昆布鹽焗鮑魚」，才算滿足。以海鮮馳名的蜑家菜館竟有「瀨尿蝦生死戀」、「手撕龍蝦燒鴨」等創意菜式？吳若希跟團發掘新口感。她又自言享受湊女過程，同時卻體會到人妻的矛盾？"},{"pid":"59cdae5f0e4b4ef7c2d6e0d346b985c288f0db10","tid":1096282,"uid":221343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"丁子朗個look同講野把聲成個6號咁"},{"pid":"688967848f6ceec8374f12bb633e50018c6e4b32","tid":1096282,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"聽日你返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaa12626fd97f29c9ac0c9fc06f805f3ed48579","tid":1096282,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"丁同泳船同年"},{"pid":"d3e76a802d08310b2069f48301541d251377f1d0","tid":1096282,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0aaa12626fd97f29c9ac0c9fc06f805f3ed48579","tid":1096282,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"丁同泳船同年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"左係咩水"},{"pid":"2a343a2e9bfec820bd4d8e51dbf6d475cdd7e935","tid":1096282,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3e76a802d08310b2069f48301541d251377f1d0","tid":1096282,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0aaa12626fd97f29c9ac0c9fc06f805f3ed48579","tid":1096282,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"丁同泳船同年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"左係咩水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"愷怡?"},{"pid":"e965d7098d529470c2c2c0d6655a400d9dad446b","tid":1096282,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"張秀文唔做學是為做呢套垃圾？"},{"pid":"2f64d75f15a086d7303990af1b45cb39